        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Luke 18:28-30",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Matthew is in part more complete (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Mark 10:28",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
