        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (at some time) ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "received, i.e.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " if the latter event does not occur, the former has not taken place; the hundredfold compensation is so certain, that its non-occurrence would presuppose the not having forsaken. The association of thought in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Mark 4:22",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (not in ",
        "children": []
